      "text": "Learning check status:\n\"got-it\" | \"needs-practice\" | \"confused\"\n\nTutor move:\n\"hint\" | \"explain\" | \"feedback\" | \"quiz\" |\n\"summary\" | \"direct_answer\" | \"clarify\"\n\nTurn intent:\n\"ask_question\" | \"answer_check\" | \"request_summary\" |\n\"request_direct_answer\" | \"practice_concept\" |\n\"translate_or_read\" | \"off_topic\"\n\nMastery update:\nscore = previous * 0.62 + observed * 0.38\nreview delay: confused=10m, needs-practice=30m/2h, got-it=1d/3d/7d",
